06/11/2009
ANKARA, Turkey -- Members of a Turkish naval ship prevented the hijacking of a Greek boat in the Gulf of Aden and detained five pirates, the army announced on Thursday (November 5th). 
The Greek boat was about 113km off the Somali coast when pirates attacked the vessel via a motor boat. 
(Reuters, Hurriyet, Zaman, ANA-MPA, Xinhua, AFP - 05/11/09)
